{
  "title": "Mac Maven 搭建",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<img src=\"quiver-image-url/99C83C57C4E45F58550379E57A95BCF6.jpg\" width=\"861\" height=\"392\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, 'SF UI Text', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><div><pre style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">mvn --version</pre></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, 'SF UI Text', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, 'SF UI Text', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Mac OS X 安装Maven:</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 22px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, 'SF UI Text', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; word-break: break-word; overflow: visible;\">下载&nbsp;<a href=\"https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(49, 148, 208); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;\">Maven</a>, 并解压到某个目录。例如/Users/robbie/apache-maven-3.3.3</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; word-break: break-word; overflow: visible;\">打开<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Terminal</code>,输入以下命令，设置<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Maven classpath</code></p><pre class=\"hljs elixir\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-word; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><code class=\"elixir\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-style: none;\"> <span class=\"hljs-variable\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(181, 137, 0);\">$ </span>vi ~<span class=\"hljs-regexp\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">/.bash_profile</span></code></pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; word-break: break-word; overflow: visible;\">添加下列两行代码，之后保存并退出<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Vi</code>：</p><pre class=\"hljs bash\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-word; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><code class=\"bash\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-style: none;\"> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 139, 210);\">export</span> M2_HOME=/Users/robbie/apache-maven-3.3.3\n <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 139, 210);\">export</span> PATH=<span class=\"hljs-variable\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(181, 137, 0);\">$PATH</span>:<span class=\"hljs-variable\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(181, 137, 0);\">$M2_HOME</span>/bin</code></pre></li></ul><div class=\"image-package\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 25px; width: 700px; margin-left: -40px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, 'SF UI Text', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/05D1B6AA11C7A4BBB307074716EFC01B.png\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/420187-6947fe0af3933d3d.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; cursor: zoom-in; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out;\" width=\"696\" height=\"478\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div class=\"image-caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; min-height: 22px; display: inline-block; padding: 10px; margin: 0px auto; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(217, 217, 217); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7;\">bash_profile</div></div><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 22px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, 'SF UI Text', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; word-break: break-word; overflow: visible;\">输入命令以使<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">bash_profile</code>生效</p><pre class=\"hljs bash\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-word; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><code class=\"bash\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-style: none;\">  <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 139, 210);\">source</span> ~/.bash_profile</code></pre></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; word-break: break-word; overflow: visible;\">输入<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">mvn -v</code>查看<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Maven</code>是否安装成功</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; word-break: break-word; overflow: visible;\">如果遇到以下异常，重新编辑<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">bash_profile</code>文件，增加<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">export JAVA_HOME=/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.7.0_11.jdk/Contents/Home</code>后，并重新运行<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">source ~/.bash_profile</code>即可。</p></li></ul><div class=\"image-package\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 25px; width: 700px; margin-left: -40px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, 'SF UI Text', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/BA56BFBEE0D403EA4A95F757AE1BDDD9.png\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/420187-21014c26d4442c05.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; cursor: zoom-in; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out;\" width=\"703\" height=\"478\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div class=\"image-caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; min-height: 22px; display: inline-block; padding: 10px; margin: 0px auto; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(217, 217, 217); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7;\">exception</div></div><div class=\"image-package\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 25px; width: 700px; margin-left: -40px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, 'SF UI Text', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/B6BC70B85E95BB936C3C69105CB911BE.png\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/420187-0b45f0a40e8da2f5.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; cursor: zoom-in; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out;\" width=\"696\" height=\"478\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div class=\"image-caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; min-height: 22px; display: inline-block; padding: 10px; margin: 0px auto; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(217, 217, 217); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7;\">new bash_profile</div></div><div class=\"image-package\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 25px; width: 700px; margin-left: -40px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, 'SF UI Text', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/FBC1A699523244B3DECF0AB689E93E3A.png\" data-original-src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/420187-fee2d6db07d70ca8.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; cursor: zoom-in; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out;\" width=\"703\" height=\"478\"></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "data": "### Creating a Maven Project（创建一个项目）\n你需要一个保存项目的文件夹，在任意路径下创建一个文件夹并在该目录下启动shell。在命令行执行下面的Maven命令：\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "c_cpp",
      "data": "mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.mycompany.app -DartifactId=my-app -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-quickstart -DinteractiveMode=false"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><em style=\"font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\">如果你仅仅只是安装了Maven，在第一次运行时将会需要等待一段时间。这是因为Maven正在下载最新的组件（插件，jar包，其他文件）到你本地的仓库。在运行成功之前，也有可能你需要多次执行以上命令。这是因为在你下载完成之前远程服务器能会响应超时。不用担心，有方法来解决这个问题。</span></em><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">你将会发现这个生成的目标会创建一个与你给定的</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 15.6px;\">artifactId的值同名的目录。进入这个目录。&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 15.6px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\">在这个目录中你会发现以下标准的项目结构。</span></p></span></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "data": "cd my-app"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 15.6px;\"></span><img src=\"quiver-image-url/70540F34C97190C4D0218A93E510F2A7.jpg\" width=\"583\" height=\"618\"></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255); font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在Maven中，pom.xml文件是一个项目配置的核心。它是一个单一的配置文件，它按你的需要包含了建立一个项目的大量信息。POM是庞大的，它的复杂性也是令人生畏的，但是你没有必要去弄懂它所有的错综复杂的东西，只需要有效地运用就行了。</span></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255); font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><h4 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Build the Project（构建项目）</h4></div><div><br></div><div><pre style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">mvn package   <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">这个命令行将会打印出各种动作，并以以下代码结束：</span></pre><pre style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><pre style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-variant-ligatures: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">...\n[INFO] ----------------------------------------------------------------\n[INFO] BUILD SUCCESSFUL\n[INFO] ------------------------------------------------------------------\n[INFO] Total time: 2 seconds\n[INFO] Finished at: Thu Jul 07 21:34:52 CEST 2011\n[INFO] Final Memory: 3M/6M\n[INFO] ------------------------------------------------------------------</pre></pre></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "data": "不像第一次执行的命令，你会发现第二个命令只是一个单词 - package。这是一个阶段而不是一个目标。一个有序的阶段是构建生命周期的一个步骤。当一个阶段被给定后，Maven将执行序列中的每一个阶段，包括一个定义。例如，如果我们执行compile 阶段，这个阶段将真正得到执行的是：1.验证 2.生成来源 3.处理来源 4.生成资源 5.处理资源 6.编译 (1.validate 2.generate-sources 3.process-sources 4.generate-resources 5.process-resources 6.compile )"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">你使用以下命令测试新编译和打包的JAR： &nbsp;</span><span style=\"orphans: 2; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">java -cp target/my-app-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar com.mycompany.app.App</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\">得到的打印结果：</span></p><p style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.3em;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" face=\"Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Hello world!</span></font></p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.3em;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" face=\"Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"></span></font></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 4px 4px 4px 24px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); font-size: 14px;\">Running Maven Tools（运行Maven工具）</h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<h4 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Maven Phases（Maven 阶段）</h4><p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\">尽管几乎没有一个全面的列表，这些都是最常见的缺省生命周期阶段执行的。</span></p><p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 12px;\"></p><ul style=\"list-style: square; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>验证&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">validate&nbsp;</strong>: 验证项目是否正确，所有必须的信息是否可用。</span></li><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>编译&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">compile&nbsp;</strong>: 编译项目的源代码。</span></li><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>测试&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">test&nbsp;</strong>: 使用合适的单元测试框架测试编译的源代码. 这些测试不应该要求代码被打包或者被部署。</span></li><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>打包&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">package&nbsp;</strong>: 把编译的代码打包成可分配的格式, 例如： JAR。</span></li><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>集成测试&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">integration-test&nbsp;</strong>:&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 15.6px;\">如果必要的话，</span>处理和部署包到一个集成测试可以运行的环境中。</span></li><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>核实&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">verify&nbsp;</strong>: 执行<span style=\"line-height: 15.6px;\">一些检查,确认包是有效的和符合质量标准的。</span></span></li><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>安装&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">install&nbsp;</strong>: 安装包到本地仓库， 作为本地其他项目的一个依赖项。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">通过</span><code style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">mvn install</code><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">命令可以将你自己的项目构建并安装到本地仓库中。这样，你的其它项目就可以通过在pom文件将该jar包作为外部依赖来使用。</span></li><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>部署&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">deploy&nbsp;</strong>: 部署到一个集成或者释放的环境中， 拷贝最终版本的包到远程仓库， 来与其他开发者和项目共享。</span></li><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255); font-size: 13px;\">这里有两个不在以上默认列表之列的Maven生命周期。他们是</span></li></ul><ul style=\"list-style: square; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\">清除&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">clean&nbsp;</strong>: 清除事先构建的组件。</span></li><li style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\">站点&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal;\">site&nbsp;</strong>: 为此项目生成站点说明文档</span></li></ul>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div class=\"section\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 4px;\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\">这个命令将会清除项目，拷贝依赖关系，和打包项目（当然会为打包执行所有阶段）。</span></p><pre style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-variant-ligatures: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">mvn clean dependency:copy-dependencies package</pre></div>"
